    HexFloatLiterals
    ImplicitPrelude
    ImportQualifiedPost
    InstanceSigs
    KindSignatures
    LambdaCase
    MonomorphismRestriction
    MultiParamTypeClasses
    NamedFieldPuns
    NamedWildCards
    NoMonomorphismRestriction
    NoStarIsType
    NumericUnderscores
    OverloadedLabels
    OverloadedRecordDot
    OverloadedStrings
    PackageImports
    PartialTypeSignatures
    PatternGuards
    PolyKinds
    PostfixOperators
