    ExplicitForAll
    FlexibleContexts
    FlexibleInstances
    ForeignFunctionInterface
    GADTSyntax
    GeneralisedNewtypeDeriving
    HexFloatLiterals
    ImplicitPrelude
    ImportQualifiedPost
    InstanceSigs
